N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 347.9 - Filing of notice

State Regulations

All notices required to be filed with the chairman, pursuant to this Subchapter, shall be deemed filed when received by the
chairman, Workers' Compensation Board, 180 Livingston Street, Brooklyn, NY
11248. Notes
